1. Select folder in Q7 explorer
2. Select "Add Tag..." in context menu
3. Set "New Tag" in the  "Select Tag(s) to Add"
4. Make sure that new tag is added in the "Tags" field for each element in this folder
5. Make sure that new tag is added in "Tags" view, and references between this tag and all elements from folder are displayed
